rComments: She seems extremely inexperienced and is obviously a very young prof. For an introductory french course it was far too advanced and very fast paced. Her lectures are not good except her detailed powerpoints and I know most of the class is confused half the time. Even if you go to all the lectures I doubt you'd learn french.
